163
00:10:58,570 --> 00:11:02,610
As soon as you were born, Choon Hee went to the hospital because the bleeding didn't stop.

164
00:11:02,610 --> 00:11:05,230
Instead of feeding my crying baby,

165
00:11:06,090 --> 00:11:08,990
