181
00:12:10,460 --> 00:12:13,240
It might seem brazen,

182
00:12:14,020 --> 00:12:18,810
but if I were to go back 30 years,

183
00:12:20,220 --> 00:12:22,180
I probably

184
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:26,300
